---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import SeoBreadcrumbs from '../../components/SeoBreadcrumbs.astro';
import enT from '../../i18n/en.json';

import grandpere from '../../assets/histoire/grandpere-yves.jpg';
import vignes from '../../assets/histoire/vignes-providence.jpg';
import kairos from '../../assets/histoire/kairos-bouteille.jpg';
import partners from '../../assets/histoire/emmanuel-claire-fred.jpg';
import bateau from '../../assets/images/photos/emmanuel-roblin-vineyard.jpg';

const t = enT;
const lang = 'en';
const frPath = '/histoire/';
const enPath = '/en/our-story/';
---

<Base
  title="Our Story — AB Initio, from the beginning"
  description="The story of AB Initio: how Emmanuel Roblin left a career in design to create organic wines in the Muscadet Nantais, Loire Valley."
  lang={lang}
  frPath={frPath}
  enPath={enPath}
>
  <Nav lang={lang} frPath={frPath} enPath={enPath} />
  <SeoBreadcrumbs items={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/en/' },
    { name: 'Our Story', url: '/en/our-story' },
  ]} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Emmanuel Roblin",
    "jobTitle": "Artisan winemaker",
    "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "AB Initio" },
    "url": "https://www.abinitio-wines.com/en/our-story"
  })} />

  <!-- 1. Hero title -->
  <div class="hero-titre">
    <span class="eyebrow">{t.storyPage.eyebrow}</span>
    <h1>{t.storyPage.title}</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. Photo + text side by side -->
  <section class="hero-histoire">
    <div class="hero-photo">
      <img src={grandpere.src} alt="Yves, Emmanuel's grandfather, fisherman" loading="eager" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="rien">For nothing happens without reason…</p>
      <div class="hero-body">
        <p><strong>October 2015, Nicolas, a friend who works in wine, takes me to a salon near Nantes.</strong> At the Domaine de l'Écu stand, Fred Niger has me taste his amphora-aged Melon de Bourgogne. The wine moves me, literally — I still remember it vividly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="text-col text-col-left">
    <p>Six months later, I join Fred at l'Écu for an internship, followed by harvest. <strong>Seized by passion, I leave a safe career in interior design and furniture to immerse myself in the dirt and the vines.</strong> The viticulture school in Amboise — at the time the only one in France specialising in organic and biodynamic farming and winemaking — introduces me to remarkable teachers: Anne-Cécile Jadaud, Damien Delecheneau, Vincent Carême, Tanguy Perraud, Philippe Chigard…</p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-col text-col-third">
    <p><strong>Harvest 2018, Fred mentions a small estate not far from l'Écu.</strong> Arriving at Domaine de la Providence, love at first sight: I fall instantly for these gnarly vines — like the century-old Melon — deeply rooted in granite and schist subsoils, and for the gentle farming practices. I move into a small house next to the cellar and start pruning.</p>
  </div>

  <img src={vignes.src} alt="The Providence vineyards at sunset, Vallet" class="vignes-break" loading="lazy" />

  <!-- Kaïros + AB Initio creation -->
  <div class="kairos-section">
    <div class="kairos-text">
      <p>The following year, the adventure truly begins: we harvest a parcel of Gamay at la Providence and make my first wine, with an amphora lent by Fred and Claire, his partner, and their administrative support. <strong>Eighteen months later, my dream becomes real: the wine is bottled. Christened Kaïros — the opportune moment, the right instant, a symbolic name for a wine born out of serendipity.</strong></p>
      <p><strong>Driven by that first success, Claire, Fred and I create AB Initio in August 2020.</strong> Me in the role of artisan winemaker — selecting the growers and the parcels, creating and crafting the wines, bringing them to market — with the indispensable material and logistical support of Fred and Claire. <strong>A range of wines born of passion, philosophy and friendship begins to take shape.</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="kairos-right">
      <img src={kairos.src} alt="Kaïros bottle, AB Initio's first cuvée" class="kairos-bottle" loading="lazy" />
      <p class="cuvees-link"><a href="/en/wines/">{t.storyPage.inlineCta}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Continuation of narrative -->
  <div class="text-col">
    <p>The beginning — <em>initio</em> — of a wine is often found in the long, meditative pruning periods, another crucial moment. Presto, a singular take on the three Nantais grapes, draws its inspiration from a field blend; Philia, the image of Breton summers at my grandfather's house, was born while pruning old Folle Blanche vines in relentless December rain.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Text column — final -->
  <div class="text-col">
    <p><strong>Little by little, a world takes shape — my world.</strong> AB Initio is the natural estuary of my life — all its currents, all its silt, all its force. A project of conviction, carrying everything that made me, everything I hold dear: my grandfather and his boat, heading out to fish in the bay of Douarnenez, along the coasts of Saint-Jean-de-Luz and Saint-Nazaire, where I was born. The ocean, an ever-present force in my family. An abundance of fish, seafood, oysters — the fabric of my childhood, naturally reflected in the personality of my wines: in their salinity, their tension, but also their breeze-like lightness. Brittany, an anchor of identity; the Muscadet, a new-found home, a terroir discovered. My philosophy studies, my need to look beneath the surface, reflected in the names of the wines, in the way I approach the vines, the wines, the people I work with. <strong>All these turning points, these encounters that move us.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <!-- Nihil -->
  <div class="nihil">
    <p>For nothing happens without reason — <em>nihil fit sine causa…</em></p>
  </div>

  <p class="author-signature">{t.storyPage.byline}</p>

  <section class="histoire-cta">
    <div class="histoire-cta-inner">
      <div class="histoire-cta-text">
        <p class="histoire-cta-title">{t.storyPage.ctaHeading}</p>
        <p class="histoire-cta-sub">{t.storyPage.ctaSub}</p>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:contact@abinitio-wines.com" class="histoire-cta-btn">{t.storyPage.ctaButton}</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Archive photos -->
  <div class="archive-photos">
    <img src={bateau.src} alt="Emmanuel Roblin in the Muscadet Nantais vineyards" loading="lazy" />
    <img src={partners.src} alt="Emmanuel Roblin, Claire Niger and Fred Niger, AB Initio partners" loading="lazy" />
  </div>

  <Footer lang={lang} frPath={frPath} enPath={enPath} />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero title */
  .hero-titre {
    background: var(--offwhite);
    text-align: center;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 8vw, 7rem) 2rem clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  .hero-titre .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: .72rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: .3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: .8rem;
  }
  .hero-titre h1 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 3.6rem);
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .author-signature {
    text-align: right;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  /* Hero — photo left, text right */
  .hero-histoire {
    background: var(--offwhite);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 42% 1fr;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem 2rem;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .hero-photo {
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  }
  .hero-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .rien {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-body {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.19rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .hero-body strong {
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero-body p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Text columns */
  .text-col {
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem .8rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.19rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    background: var(--offwhite);
  }
  .text-col p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .text-col strong {
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .text-col em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .text-col-left {
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .text-col-third {
    padding-top: .5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Kaïros section */
  .kairos-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--offwhite);
  }
  .kairos-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.19rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
  }
  .kairos-text strong {
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .kairos-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .kairos-bottle {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    padding-top: 48px;
  }

  /* Vignes break */
  .vignes-break {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 21 / 9;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Nihil */
  .nihil {
    text-align: right;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 3rem 3rem;
    background: var(--offwhite);
  }
  .nihil p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.56rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: .05em;
  }

  /* Archive photos */
  .archive-photos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .archive-photos img {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Histoire CTA */
  .histoire-cta {
    background: var(--accent);
    padding: 64px 48px;
  }
  .histoire-cta-inner {
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .histoire-cta-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 260px;
  }
  .histoire-cta-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--offwhite);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .histoire-cta-sub {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: .88rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--offwhite);
    opacity: .7;
  }
  .histoire-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--offwhite);
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 235, .3);
    transition: all .3s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .histoire-cta-btn:hover {
    background: var(--offwhite);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Cuvées link */
  .cuvees-link {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .cuvees-link a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .cuvees-link a:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-titre {
      padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-histoire {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 0 1.5rem 2rem;
    }
    .hero-photo {
      padding-right: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-photo img {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    }
    .text-col {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .vignes-break {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    }
    .kairos-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 0 1.5rem 2rem;
    }
    .kairos-bottle {
      aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
    }
    .nihil {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    }
    .archive-photos {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
